# VolleyVision frontend environment variables
#
# API base URL for the backend.
# Leave unset in local development — the default '/api/v1' goes through the
# Vite dev proxy (see vite.config.ts). Set an absolute URL when the frontend
# is served from a different origin than the API (e.g. a deployed SPA or the
# future mobile client).
#
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.example.com/api/v1
